ipolisi yeemfihlelo yeGoogle


;Am I being tracked as I browse the web?
Ngaba ndiyetrekwa njengoko ndibhrawa iwebhu?


;No. Firefox only requests a location when a website makes a request, and only shares your location when the user has approved the request. Firefox does not track or remember your location as you browse.
Hayi. IFirefox kuphela icela indawo xa iwebhsayithi isenza isicelo, ize ichaze kuphela indawo yakho xa umsebenzisi egunyazise isicelo. IFirefox ayitreki okanye ikhumbule indawo okuyo njengoko ubhrawza.


;How do I undo a permission granted to a site?
Ndiyicima njani imvume enikwe isayithi?


;If you've given Firefox permission to always give your location to a site and later change your mind, you can easily revoke that permission. Here's how:
Ukuba unike iFirefox imvume yokusoloko uchaza indawo okuyo kwisayithi uze kamva utshintshe ingqondo, unokuthi ngokulula uyicime loo mvume. Ungayenza ngolu hlobo:


