Ndiyicima njani “inombolo yesazisi yomthengi yesiquphe”?


;Go to the <em>Tools</em> menu, then select <em>Clear Recent History</em>
Yiya kwi <em>Tools</em> menu, uze ukhethe <em>Clear Recent History</em>


;Click the <em>Details</em> arrow
Cofa <em>utolo</em> lweeNkcukacha


